article.description: — Mike Okauru scored 17 points as UNC Wilmington beat Campbell 78-59 on Monday.
article.headline: Okauru lifts UNC Wilmington past Campbell 78-59
article.linkText: Okauru lifts UNC Wilmington past Campbell 78-59
article.story: BUIES CREEK, N.C. -- — Mike Okauru scored 17 points as UNC Wilmington beat Campbell 78-59 on Monday. Jaylen Sims and Ty Gadsden added 15 points, and Joe Pridgen had 14 points and 13 rebounds for UNC Wilmington (5-3). Cedric Henderson Jr. had 23 points and nine rebounds for the Fighting Camels (4-3). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
